data.description: Escape to the ultimate Colorado living experience in this exceptional 4574-square-foot custom home, where every detail reflects a new way of life. Bid farewell to the ordinary and embrace the extraordinary in Bear Creek Ranchettes, one of Colorado's hidden gems. This luxury golf course property offers sweeping views of the majestic Mountains and is walking distance to The Homestead Golf Course and Fox Hollow Golf Course. Immerse yourself in the serenity of country living, where you can ride your horse or mountain bike directly from your doorstep into the breathtaking Bear Creek Lake Park. This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to own an acreage property in such an idyllic setting. The charm of this beautiful custom 2-story home is evident from the moment you enter. The gourmet kitchen features a spacious center island, and custom cabinets with abundant storage, seamlessly connecting to the family room and formal dining area perfect for entertaining friends and family. With 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, a 3 Car Attached Garage, 6 Car Detached Garage/Barn, RV Parking and an office, this home offers ample space for all your needs. The main floor primary bedroom is a retreat with a very oversized walk-in closet and a spa-like 5 piece primary bathroom. An additional bedroom on the main floor is ideal for infants or parents. Upstairs, discover 2 bedrooms, a Jack & Jill bath, and a fantastic bonus room with views of the Fox Hollow Course and the breathtaking mountains. Imagine starting your day by riding horses, enjoying a lunchtime paddle-boarding adventure, and going mountain biking right from your own backyard. Last, the Detached Garage/Barn features 2 Stalls/Room for 5 Cars, Hay Storage, Electricity & Water. Seize the chance to redefine your lifestyle and make this extraordinary property yours. Don't just dream of the Colorado lifestyle; live it in this remarkable luxury home.
